title: So about the server transfers, whats going on?
body: They announced the transfers would be up 2 months ago and the new season is starting in a day and we still have no updates, whats going on?

replies.body: HollyMonster was actually able to provide updates not that long ago in her [**original post over here**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/rlu6awv4-transfer-service-update).
Well, we only know late january and early february, no more details :P
